<body>
    <h1>Mover (Associate) (Use Case =E2=80=93 UC03)</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"Mover(Associate)(UseCase=E2=80=93UC03)-Moverworkflow">Mov=
er workflow</h3>
<p>Table-19</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"6=
8930422-b162-42f7-9419-f8e78d28f0ab" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 317.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1482.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Mover&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The Mover use case describes the process to automatically update and adj=
ust access privileges in SailPoint when a user moves within the organizatio=
n.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of Attributes&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following set of attributes represent the tentative set of users=E2=
=80=99 attributes which will be used in the process flow. The final set of =
source and target attributes will be finalized in the solution design docum=
ent.</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Person Number</p></li>
<li>
<p>Assignment Status&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>System Worker Type&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Assignment ID</p></li>
<li>
<p>Action Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Effective start date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Effective end date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Department&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Position&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Location&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ministry&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Workrelationship Primary Flag</p></li>
<li>
<p>BU&nbsp;(business unit)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Jobcode</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Refer Appendix =E2=80=9C<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://drive=
.google.com/drive/folders/17u4oN4VdyLijziIcn8PMSlUxT5HS_LW0" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>Source and Target Attribute Mapping</u></a>=E2=80=9D for complete lis=
t of attribute mapping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Conditions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>User is already present in SailPoint IdentityIQ with its current account=
s and access details.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>When following conditions are true:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Change in attributes BU/Department/Jobcode/location values in Oracle HR =
system.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Assignment status</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should be=
 equal to =E2=80=98<strong>Active - Payroll Eligible</strong>=E2=80=99.</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>System Worker Type</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should b=
e equal to =E2=80=98<strong>Associate</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Action Name</strong>=E2=80=99 attributes value should e=
qual to =E2=80=98<strong>Position Synchronization</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p>Assignment <strong>Effective Start Date</strong> should match with <stro=
ng>Current date</strong>.&nbsp;</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Change in attributes BU/Department/Jobcode/location values in Oracle HR =
system.</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint will automatically revoke existing access which is not needed =
based on new user profile data. No birthright access will be removed.</p></=
li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will provision new access based on new Jobcode/ loc=
ation/ BU/Department</p></li>
<li>
<p>No approval will be obtained for the mover steps processing.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of downstream applications</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Active Directory, Azure, GSuite, ServiceNow, Oracle ERP Cloud, Oracle EP=
M Cloud, OCI.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ should automatically revoke not needed existing acc=
ess and SailPoint IdentityIQ will provision new access based on the new Job=
code/ location/ BU/Department.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>A ServiceNow ticket will be created and assigned to the Ascension Health=
 Alliance SailPoint IIQ support team.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Persona / Actors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Automated Process</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Dependency:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"819" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"99=
d78bf0-22b1-4b85-9a8a-d7d786dd3f00" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 70.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 174.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 575.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>S. no</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Dependency</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Point of contact for answers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of attributes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to send the final set of attributes ma=
pping</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required for trigger</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required in the Basic Flow</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>4</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ascension Health Alliance team to confirm the list of birthright access =
applications based on new values</p>
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to provide users=E2=80=99 demographic =
information and access mapping for mover:</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
